cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a neural machine translation model. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing an intelligent system for language translation. The use of attention mechanisms in the proposed model also suggests it could be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions using image captioning as a potential application, which could place it under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
